    "Id": "chassisdef_hai_SFH-2",
    "Name": "Hai",
    "Details": "Based heavily on the Uziel 8S, the Hai enhances the medium ‘Mech’s performance with a Sea Fox XL engine and Clan-spec weaponry, increasing durability and firepower. Its extra 10 tons allow for an Angel ECM suite and CASE II armor integrated into Light Ferro-Fibrous plating. Though slightly hotter running, the Hai carries more armor and retains similar mobility. The extended weapon range lets it skirmish at safer distances, avoiding close-range damage. Offensively, eight Improved Jump Jets boost maneuverability, while four Clan Medium Pulse Lasers and a Streak SRM 6 launcher, supported by one ton of ammo, deliver lethal mid-range strikes.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Tacticon TC7000</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>\n\n<b><color=#0064e6>Used with permission from Aries Games and Miniatures.</color></b>",
