  "YangsThoughts": "The Hai is a heavy cavalry 'Mech born from Lyran desperation and Sea Fox negotiation. Produced by Defiance Industries in 3140, it’s a joint effort that gave both sides what they wanted—advanced firepower and profit. Based on the Uziel 8S, the Hai uses a Sea Fox XL engine and Clan-spec weapons to deliver superior range and damage. Heavier than its predecessor, it can take and deal more punishment, making it a valuable asset in modern combat.",
